## Version pins

Confirm APIs against `gradle/libs.versions.toml` before suggesting deprecated patterns (e.g. Voyager is catalogued but **unused** — navigation is custom `AppNavigator`).

When suggesting a dependency upgrade, note breaking changes from release notes and run unit + instrumented compile after bump.
